title: Days of our Lives S52E172 Monday, May 22, 2017
description:
Sonny and Paul jump Guy and deliver him into JJ’s custody.



Nicole and Eric put aside their differences and agree to work together to try to escape.



Deimos is angry to learn he’s been tricked, but must turn his attention to his main agenda.



Ciara is horrified to learn of Theo and Wyatt’s lie
